 --------------------------------------------
\end{lstlisting}
\normalsize
Rate ratio, RR = $38.89/26.12 = 1.49$, \\
Std. error of log-RR, SE  = $\sqrt{1/748 + 1/797} = 0.051$, \\
Error factor, EF = $\exp(1.96 \times 0.051) = 1.105$, \\
95\% confidence interval for RR:\\
$(1.49/1.105, 1.49\times 1.105) =
 (1.35, 1.64)$.
